SELECT it.timestamp, gc.latitude, gc.longitude FROM ImageTimestamps it JOIN ImageGeotags ig ON it.image_id = ig.image_id JOIN GpsCoordinates gc ON ig.gps_id = gc.gps_id WHERE gc.latitude > 0 AND gc.longitude < 0 ORDER BY it.timestamp ASC;

SELECT ig.image_id, gc.latitude, gc.longitude, it.timestamp FROM ImageGeotags ig JOIN GpsCoordinates gc ON ig.gps_id = gc.gps_id JOIN ImageTimestamps it ON ig.image_id = it.image_id WHERE gc.latitude BETWEEN 35.0 AND 40.0 AND gc.longitude BETWEEN -120.0 AND -100.0 ORDER BY it.timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT ig.image_id, gc.latitude, gc.longitude, it.timestamp FROM ImageGeotags ig JOIN GpsCoordinates gc ON ig.gps_id = gc.gps_id JOIN ImageTimestamps it ON ig.image_id = it.image_id WHERE it.timestamp > '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND gc.latitude < 50.0 ORDER BY it.timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT it.image_id, it.timestamp FROM ImageTimestamps it LEFT JOIN ImageGeotags ig ON it.image_id = ig.image_id WHERE ig.gps_id IS NULL ORDER BY it.timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT image_metadata.title, image_timestamps.timestamp, locations.latitude FROM image_metadata JOIN image_timestamps ON image_metadata.image_id = image_timestamps.image_id JOIN locations ON image_timestamps.location_id = locations.location_id;

SELECT image_metadata.title, image_timestamps.timestamp, locations.latitude, locations.longitude FROM image_metadata JOIN image_timestamps ON image_metadata.image_id = image_timestamps.image_id JOIN locations ON image_timestamps.location_id = locations.location_id WHERE locations.latitude > 40;

SELECT image_metadata.title, image_timestamps.timestamp, image_keywords.keyword_id, keywords.keyword FROM image_metadata JOIN image_timestamps ON image_metadata.image_id = image_timestamps.image_id JOIN image_keywords ON image_timestamps.image_id = image_keywords.image_id JOIN keywords ON image_keywords.keyword_id = keywords.keyword_id;

SELECT image_metadata.title, image_timestamps.timestamp, locations.latitude, locations.longitude, keywords.keyword FROM image_metadata JOIN image_timestamps ON image_metadata.image_id = image_timestamps.image_id JOIN locations ON image_timestamps.location_id = locations.location_id JOIN image_keywords ON image_timestamps.image_id = image_keywords.image_id JOIN keywords ON image_keywords.keyword_id = keywords.keyword_id ORDER BY image_timestamps.timestamp DESC;
